HEADWORD: Blazoner
<hw>Bla"zon*er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who gives
publicity, proclaims, or blazons; esp., one who blazons coats of arms; a
herald.</def> <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

